should handle concurrent profile requests
should work through Traefik proxy

should maintain consistent response format
should handle network errors gracefully
should return proper HTTP status codes
should include appropriate CORS headers
should authenticate once and access all services

specs.title: should handle profile access after login with remember me
should redirect to login when not authenticated
should show profile page when authenticated with JWT cookies
should display profile page structure correctly
should contain all required profile elements
should display account actions sidebar
should load JavaScript configuration correctly
should initialize API client correctly
should load profile data automatically
should handle refresh button functionality
should handle API errors gracefully
should retry after API error
should fail gracefully when no JWT token is accessible to JavaScript
should successfully load profile with correct cookie setup
should not expose sensitive information
should handle invalid JWT tokens
should have working logout functionality
should have working refresh page functionality
should display service information correctly
should be responsive on mobile devices
should be responsive on tablet devices
